### Profile Bounded Context API
### Base URL: https://localhost:5001/api

@baseUrl = https://localhost:5001/api
@contentType = application/json
@token = your-jwt-token-here

### Create Consumer Profile
POST {{baseUrl}}/profiles/consumer
Content-Type: {{contentType}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "firstName": "John",
  "lastName": "Doe",
  "phoneNumber": "+1234567890"
}

### Get Consumer Profile
GET {{baseUrl}}/profiles/consumer/{{profileId}}
Content-Type: {{contentType}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Update Consumer Profile
PUT {{baseUrl}}/profiles/consumer
Content-Type: {{contentType}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "profileId": "{{profileId}}",
  "firstName": "John",
  "lastName": "Doe",
  "phoneNumber": "+1234567890",
  "street": "123 Main St",
  "city": "New York",
  "state": "NY",
  "country": "USA",
  "zipCode": "10001"
}

### Create Business Profile
POST {{baseUrl}}/profiles/business
Content-Type: {{contentType}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "businessName": "ACME Corporation",
  "taxId": "12-3456789",
  "category": {
    "name": "Retail",
    "description": "Retail business"
  }
}

### Get Business Profile
GET {{baseUrl}}/profiles/business/{{profileId}}
Content-Type: {{contentType}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Update Business Profile
PUT {{baseUrl}}/profiles/business
Content-Type: {{contentType}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "profileId": "{{profileId}}",
  "businessName": "ACME Corporation",
  "category": "Retail",
  "description": "Leading retail business",
  "street": "456 Business Ave",
  "city": "Los Angeles",
  "state": "CA",
  "country": "USA",
  "zipCode": "90001"
}

### Submit Business Verification
POST {{baseUrl}}/verification/submit
Content-Type: {{contentType}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "profileId": "{{profileId}}",
  "documentUrl": "https://storage.example.com/documents/business-license-12345.pdf"
}

### Approve Business Verification (Admin Only)
POST {{baseUrl}}/verification/approve
Content-Type: {{contentType}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "profileId": "{{profileId}}",
  "documentUrl": "https://storage.example.com/documents/business-license-12345.pdf"
}

### Get Pending Verification Profiles (Admin Only)
GET {{baseUrl}}/admin/profiles/pending-verification?pageNumber=1&pageSize=10
Content-Type: {{contentType}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Get User Profiles (Admin Only)
GET {{baseUrl}}/admin/profiles/by-user/{{userId}}
Content-Type: {{contentType}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
